        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Employee Privacy Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits employers from inquiring about the vaccination status of employees or prospective employees.</p> <p>Violations of this prohibition are subject to civil penalties, special damages, and injunctive relief as appropriate.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
